QuestData.Title: Sometimes Less Is More
QuestData.Description:
I don't really hate saurolisk, but there seem to be a lot more around lately.
Stormsong's military used to thin out the population, but they didn't show up this year.
Maybe you could do the job they didn't!
QuestData.CompletionText: I still see a lot of Saurolisk around.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you. I can rest easy knowing they are safe.
